KZN Premier Sihle Zikala is leading a delegation meeting with farmers in Newcastle. Courtesy #DStv403 NEWCASTLE - KwaZulu Natal Premier Sihle Zikala is leading a delegation meeting with farmers in Newcastle. There are growing concerns about farm safety in the area. READ: Farm Murders: DA calls for govt to tackle crimes The Newcastle community took to the streets earlier this month against farm murders. The protests follow the deaths of farming couple Glen and Vida Rafferty.